text:
I had issues connecting to my wordpress admin page where a http 404 message was displayed instead of admin login page.
I was connected to Avinash from misshosting support. Avinash had a polite and modest approach which i liked. Even though i had difficulties from my side, Avinash showed patience and worked together with me to ensure that i got satisfied.
Thank you for the help Avinash!
Best Regards
